<!DOCTYPE html>
    <html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Error 429 - Too Many Requests</title>
        <style>
            body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; padding: 50px; }
            .message { padding: 20px; background-color: #ffdddd; border: 1px solid #ffcccc; margin: 20px 0; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Error 429 - Too Many Requests</h1>
        <div class="message">
            <p>The server received too many requests within a short period of time. Please wait a few seconds and refresh the page.</p>
            <p>If the issue persists, feel free to contact <a href="mailto:{{maintainers}}">{{maintainers}}</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>